The evidence with the title 'U.S. solar jobs rose 24.5% to surpass fossil fuel power plant ... ' says Feb 7, 2017  ... The U.S. solar industry employed 260077 workers last year , a 24.5% increase from 2015 driven by a rise in rooftop solar installations .  ... The solar jobs census follows a U.S. Department Of Energy study released last month that found more Americans work in solar than at natural gas or coal power plants . 
